sequenceDiagram
    participant Main as 主线程 (main)
    participant RT as libcudart
    participant Drv as libcuda.so
    participant KO as nvidia.ko
    participant GPU as GPU
    participant Worker as Worker 线程

    Main->>RT: cudaDeviceSynchronize()
    RT->>Drv: cuCtxSynchronize_v2()
    loop 排空各 Stream
        Drv->>KO: ioctl(0x2b) fence 查询
        Drv->>Worker: write(eventfd, 8B)
        Main->>Main: futex(WAIT_BITSET)
        GPU-->>KO: 完成中断 (MSI)
        KO-->>Worker: eventfd 可读
        Worker->>Worker: poll + read(eventfd)
        Worker->>Main: futex(WAKE)
    end
    loop 最终 fence 确认
        Drv->>KO: ioctl(0x2b) × 3
        KO->>GPU: 读 fence 寄存器
        GPU-->>KO: 全部完成
    end
    Drv-->>RT: 成功
    RT-->>Main: 返回
